==Behind the Scenes==
*During development of the [[Loki (TV series)/Season One|first season]] of ''[[Loki (TV series)|Loki]]'', B-15 was originally conceived as a male character named Hunter 9K. 9K was imagined as an angry person with enhanced strength and a retro futuristic look. The character's gender and personality changed once [[Wunmi Mosaku]] read for the part and gave the character more sass.{{Ref|TAoLK}}
*[[Marché Day]] was a stunt double for [[Wunmi Mosaku]] in the role of B-15.

